@supportURL   https://github.com/Pwuts/modern-mediasite/issues
@updateURL    https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Pwuts/modern-mediasite/master/Mediasite.user.css
@author       Pwuts <pwuts@pwuts.nl> (https://github.com/Pwuts)
